1.Download this Minecraft hack client https://www.mediafire.com/file/o91g4ix9v4ozu47/Jigsaw_0.26.zip/file
2.Join any Minecraft server that has a forum where you can report bugs.
3.Download a high FPS desktop recorders likeOBS, Bandicam & etc
4.Now to open the hack GUI to close it just press ESC.
5.Find the "World" module, right click it to see the things you can do with the module, after that find "FakeHackers" then enable it.
6.In your chat box type .fakehacker <target_player_name>
This will make the target player a hacker.

Now. To ban him type the command press "P" to hide the hack client, and make a bind key in your desktop recorder to record now just record him then after you record him a few minutes stop the recorder.
Double check the recorded video if they are any hack client that is enabled so the staff that will review the video won't suspect that your faking your video.
If they check the video is all normal they will ban the player for hacking :)
